33/*
34 * RFC1826/2402 authentication header.
35 */
36
37#ifndef _NETINET6_AH_H_
38#define _NETINET6_AH_H_
39
40struct ah {
41 uint8_t ah_nxt; /* Next Header */
42 uint8_t ah_len; /* Length of data, in 32bit */
43 uint16_t ah_reserve; /* Reserved for future use */
44 uint32_t ah_spi; /* Security parameter index */
45 /* variable size, 32bit bound*/ /* Authentication data */
46};
47
48struct newah {
49 uint8_t ah_nxt; /* Next Header */
50 uint8_t ah_len; /* Length of data + 1, in 32bit */
51 uint16_t ah_reserve; /* Reserved for future use */
52 uint32_t ah_spi; /* Security parameter index */
53 uint32_t ah_seq; /* Sequence number field */
54 /* variable size, 32bit bound*/ /* Authentication data */
55};
56
57#endif /*_NETINET6_AH_H_*/
